pageContext.title: Tokyo Rising Sun - Lowland
pageContext.description: A forgotten gem in the deepest, darkest corner of the warehouse. Aged in a Lowland whisky cask resulting in decadent chocolate, toasted vanilla, indulgent spiced fruit, a mesmerizingly hypnotic mouthfeel and new layers that emerge on every sip.
pageContext.author: Sam Mason <samjbmason>
